item.title: Eric Adams endorses Andrew Cuomo in NYC mayor's race
item.description: Adams and Cuomo appeared at NYCHA's Carver Houses Thursday afternoon. Cuomo embraced Adams as they met.

item.title: Thousands of Starbucks workers could be set to go on strike
